text:
Thursday Night Preview, District Play Begins Kyle Henderson NMPreps.com Publisher 
Today we preview the Week 7 Thursday Night match ups which take place across New Mexico. District play begins, Mayfield takes on Onate and Valley takes on West Mesa. 
Onate vs. Mayfield (Field of Dreams) The Knights may have started 0-4 this season, but have won their last two match ups running... Continue Reading Here 
West Mesa @ Valley (Community) This was supposed to be one West Mesa's best teams in years, but at 1-5 their preseason hype was just... Continue Reading Here 
Bernalillo @ Del Norte (Milne) While the talk in district 2-5A is focused on Espanola and Capital, those teams would likely also sit at 2-4... Continue Reading Here 
Clovis JV @ Texico It's been hard to gauge Texico this season. One week they beat Santa Rosa, then lose to Tucumcari... Continue Reading Here Talk about it in NEW MEXICO PREP FOOTBALL INSIDER FEATURED PRODUCT
